---

## ðŸ“ž Quick Reference

**Project ID**: accreditex-79c08
**Collection**: appSettings
**Document ID**: default
**Settings File**: appSettings.json (in project root)

**Commands**:
```bash
# Install
npm install -g firebase-tools

# Login
firebase login

# Upload (from project root)
firebase --project=accreditex-79c08 firestore:set appSettings/default --merge < appSettings.json

# Verify
firebase --project=accreditex-79c08 firestore:get appSettings/default
```

